latestIgtvVideos.title: STORE EXPERIENCE AT FOREVER21 ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I was hesitant to step out for my usual whirlwind round of Pujo shopping this year… Finally I decided to go over to Forever21. It was a fantastic decision! 🙈 
The clothes were to die for, there were fabulous offers – check the offer on handbags worth Rs 7000 from the Kylie and Kendall collection,for a shopping of only Rs 3500!!! 😍
And the best part? I was able to browse, try out loads of outfits at the trial rooms… all with ease! Safety protocols were followed strictly with no exceptions! So go on, shop lots, shop safe at Forever 21! ❤️

@forever21_in

Store: Forever 21, GS Road Guwahati 

#Forever21 #Pujo #PujoShopping #SpecialOffers #SafeShopping #StoreHygiene #SafetyProtocol

latestPosts.caption:
Still wrapping my head around the fact that my bff just got married! 🥹
@choudhury_sagarika & @chinmaynagrecha’s wedding wasn’t just a celebration - it was a rollercoaster of emotions, laughter, happy tears, and endless dancing! 😜
Watching my Bestie step into this beautiful new chapter with someone as wonderful as Chinmay filled my heart in ways words can’t explain.
From childhood secrets to grown-up milestones, we’ve been through it all… and now we’re both married within 6 months of each other. Life really came full circle, didn’t it?
What a ride it’s been - and it’s only getting better from here. 😘

Here’s to forever love, inside jokes, and dancing till 3 AM ! 💃🏻😂

All I wanted was this dance and he delivered! 🤣🧿

At @choudhury_sagarika & @chinmaynagrecha’s sangeet. ♥️

[couple dance, sangeet, Indian wedding, couple, biwi no. 1]
